testsuite.name: GenericRepository sortByIdentity Tests

testcase.name: sortByIdentity on empty repository should return empty list
sortByIdentity with null order should default to 'asc'
sortByIdentity should be case-insensitive for order parameter
sortByIdentity should not modify the original repository
sortByIdentity with invalid order should default to 'asc'
sortByIdentity with single element should return list with that element
sortByIdentity with duplicate identities should maintain stability
sortByIdentity with 'desc' should sort in descending order
sortByIdentity should return reverse order for asc and desc
sortByIdentity with 'asc' should sort in ascending order
